            <title>[TIKA-4189] CallablePipesIterator should pause for &quot;timeoutMillis&quot; amount on offering completed semaphore</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-4189</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
